---
---

<div class="overflow-hidden bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl md:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-16 gap-x-8 sm:gap-y-20 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-start"
    >
      <div class="px-6 md:px-0 lg:pt-4 lg:pr-4">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-lg">
          <h2
            class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-green-600"
          >
            Performance
          </h2>
          <p
            class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl"
          >
            Build faster apps
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
            Aptahub makes it easier for you to find what is causing your app to
            be slow.
          </p>
          <dl
            class="mt-10 max-w-xl space-y-8 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 lg:max-w-none"
          >
            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                <svg
                  class="absolute top-1 left-1 h-5 w-5"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M7.5 14.25v2.25m3-4.5v4.5m3-6.75v6.75m3-9v9M6 20.25h12A2.25 2.25 0 0020.25 18V6A2.25 2.25 0 0018 3.75H6A2.25 2.25 0 003.75 6v12A2.25 2.25 0 006 20.25z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
                Reports
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">
                Generate performance reports by device, OS or app version so you
                can troubleshoot it more easily.
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  class="absolute top-1 left-1 h-5 w-5"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M2.25 18L9 11.25l4.306 4.307a11.95 11.95 0 015.814-5.519l2.74-1.22m0 0l-5.94-2.28m5.94 2.28l-2.28 5.941"
                  ></path>
                </svg>

                Trends
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">
                Find performance degradation over time before it becomes a
                problem.
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  class="absolute top-1 left-1 h-5 w-5"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M8.288 15.038a5.25 5.25 0 017.424 0M5.106 11.856c3.807-3.808 9.98-3.808 13.788 0M1.924 8.674c5.565-5.565 14.587-5.565 20.152 0M12.53 18.22l-.53.53-.53-.53a.75.75 0 011.06 0z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
                Traces
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">
                Be it a network request, a database query or a function call,
                with Aptahub SDK you can monitor anything you want.
              </dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sm:px-6 lg:px-0">
        <div
          class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-green-500 px-6 pt-8 sm:mx-auto sm:max-w-2xl sm:rounded-3xl sm:pt-16 sm:pl-16 sm:pr-0 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-y-px -left-3 -z-10 w-full origin-bottom-left skew-x-[-30deg] bg-green-100 opacity-20 ring-1 ring-inset ring-white"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl sm:mx-0 sm:max-w-none">
            <img
              src="/modules/performance.png"
              class="w-full rounded-xl lg:w-auto lg:max-w-4xl mb-4"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 ring-1 ring-inset ring-black/10 sm:rounded-3xl"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
